- Bug Report Interface
- Upgrade the dependency to GLib 2.32 when it is available on Debian Wheezy,
  and use new threads API in newer GLib
- Upgrade the dependency to GTK+ 3.4 when it is available on Debian Wheezy
- Make some widgets hidable (e.g. cover image, lyric label, spectrum show)
